    {
      "Text": "Security update for the Linux Kernel RT (Live Patch 18 for SUSE Linux Enterprise Micro 6.0)",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "\nThis update for the SUSE Linux Enterprise Kernel 6.4.0-40.1 fixes various security issues\n\nThe following security issues were fixed:\n\n- CVE-2026-23204: net/sched: cls_u32: use skb_header_pointer_careful() (bsc#1259126).\n- CVE-2026-31431: crypto: algif_aead - Revert to operating out-of-place (bsc#1263689).\n\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
